3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with analyzing facial expressions in visual data. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new model for recognizing human emotions, which is a subfield of AI. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper deals with recognizing human emotions, which is an important aspect of HCI.
